description: Fastator AB engages in the business of real estate. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 130 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2012-04-23. The firm focuses on financing property projects, as well as investing in real estate-related entities through active and long-term ownership. Its investment range includes listed and unlisted entities. The company acquires minority stake ownership in portfolio firms. Furthermore, the Company supports entities business development and implementation of investment opportunities.
naicsSubsector: Securities, Commodity Contracts, and Other Financial Investments and Related Activities
